events.name: Tennessee Volunteers at Alabama Crimson Tide

headlines.description: Bo Scarbrough had two fourth-down touchdown runs and No. 1 Alabama continued its domination of rival Tennessee with a 45-7 victory on Saturday.

events.name: Michigan Wolverines at Penn State Nittany Lions

headlines.description: Saquon Barkley and Trace McSorley cut through Michigan's stingy defense, each scoring three touchdowns, and No. 2 Penn State emphatically avenged its last regular-season loss with a 42-13 victory against the 19th-ranked Wolverines on Saturday night.

events.name: Kansas Jayhawks at TCU Horned Frogs

events.name: Maryland Terrapins at Wisconsin Badgers
